uk.co.jemos.podam.api

Class RandomDataProviderStrategyImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.jemos.podam.api.AbstractRandomDataProviderStrategy
      • uk.co.jemos.podam.api.RandomDataProviderStrategyImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataProviderStrategy, RandomDataProviderStrategy

    @ThreadSafe
public final class RandomDataProviderStrategyImpl
extends AbstractRandomDataProviderStrategy
    Default implementation of a DataProviderStrategy

    This default implementation returns values based on a random generator. Don't use this implementation if you seek deterministic values

    All values returned by this implementation are different from zero.

    This implementation is a Singleton

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    mtedone
